'''森林小丘-71大道車站'''（{{lang-en|Forest Hills–71st Avenue station}}），曾稱「71-大陸大道車站」（{{lang-en|71st–Continental Avenues station}}），是[[紐約地鐵|紐約地鐵]][[IND皇后林蔭路線|IND皇后林蔭路線]]的一個快車[[地鐵站|地鐵站]]，位於[[皇后區|皇后區]][[森林小丘|森林小丘]][[皇后林蔭路|皇后林蔭路]]與71大道、大陸大道交汇处，設有[[紐約地鐵E線|E線]]與[[紐約地鐵F線|F線]]（任何時候停站）、[[紐約地鐵R線|R線]]（任何時候停站，包括深夜）、[[紐約地鐵M線|M線]]（僅平日停站）列車服務。同時此站通常也是後兩者的[[總站|總站]]。

== 歷史 ==
皇后林蔭路線是紐約市擁有的[[獨立地鐵系統|獨立地鐵系統]]其中一條首先興建的路線<ref name="NYTimes-OurGreatSubway-IND2ndSystem-1929">{{cite web|url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9C0CE4D71530E73ABC4A51DFBF668382639EDE|title=OUR GREAT SUBWAY NETWORK SPREADS WIDER; New Plans of Board of Transportation Involve the Building of More Than One Hundred Miles of Additional Rapid Transit Routes for New York|date=1929-09-22|publisher=[[紐約時報|The New York Times]]|last1=Duffus|first1=R.L.|accessdate=2015-08-19|archive-date=2015-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150927200458/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9C0CE4D71530E73ABC4A51DFBF668382639EDE|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NYTimes-QBL-AheadSched-1929">{{cite web|url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9907EFDD113EE73ABC4F53DFB2668382639EDE|title=QUEENS SUBWAY WORK AHEAD OF SCHEDULE: Completion Will Lead to Big Apartrnent Building, Says William C. Speers.|date=1929-04-07|publisher=[[紐約時報|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2015-09-01|archive-date=2015-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150927225841/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9907EFDD113EE73ABC4F53DFB2668382639EDE|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BklynEagle-QnsBestBoro-1929">{{cite web|url=https://www.newspapers.com/image/58266784/?terms=%22178th%22%2Bsubway%2Bqueens|title=Queens Lauded as Best Boro By Chamber Chief|date=1929-09-23|via={{link-en|Newspapers.com|Newspapers.com}}|newspaper={{link-en|布魯克林每日鷹報|Brooklyn Daily Eagle|Brooklyn Daily Eagle}}|page=40|accessdate=2015-10-04|archive-date=2016-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161026232315/https://www.newspapers.com/image/58266784/?terms=%22178th%22%2Bsubway%2Bqueens|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由曼哈頓[[IND第八大道線|IND第八大道線]]一直延至[[皇后區|皇后區]]{{link-en|牙買加 (皇后區)|Jamaica, Queens|牙買加}}的[[牙買加-179街車站_(IND皇后林蔭路線)|179街及山邊大道]]<ref name="NYTimes-OurGreatSubway-IND2ndSystem-1929" /><ref name="BklynEagle-QnsBestBoro-1929" /><ref name="NYTimes-HylanSubway-CulverCrstwnQBL-1925">[[紐約時報|New York Times]], [https://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive/pdf?res=9C05E3DE133FE733A25752C2A9659C946495D6CF New Subway Routes in Hylan Program to Cost $186,046,000], March 21, 1925, page 1</ref>。皇后林蔭路線作為[[公共工程管理|公共工程管理]]貸款的一部分，並花費2500萬美元<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9A0CE6D6173EEE3BBC4851DFB467838D629EDE|title=TEST TRAINS RUNNING IN QUEENS SUBWAY; Switch and Signal Equipment of New Independent Line Is Being Checked.|date=1936-12-20|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-04-26|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305174522/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9A0CE6D6173EEE3BBC4851DFB467838D629EDE|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其中一個計劃中車站位於71大道上。1920年代末，地鐵延伸的新聞影響下，房地產價格飆升，舊大廈被拆除以騰出空間進行新發展<ref name=":0">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=yfz7w8mogvEC|title=Forest Hills|last=Hirshon|first=Nicholas|last2=Romano|first2=Foreword by Ray|date=2013-01-01|publisher=Arcadia Publishing|isbn=9780738597850|language=en}}</ref>。1930年皇后林蔭路線興建的期待引致的升幅，更引致了皇后林蔭路沿路若干街區重新劃區，以便興建15層公寓大廈<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9C03E0DE153AE532A25750C2A9659C946194D6CF|title=QUEENS TO HAVE 15-STORY HOUSE; Tall Structure for New Residential Development in ForestHills Area.NEAR BOULEVARD SUBWAYSeveral Blocks Rezoned for High Buildings Between Jamaicaand Kew Gardens. Apartment Height's Increase.|date=1930-03-23|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-04-26|archive-date=2016-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509205608/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9C03E0DE153AE532A25750C2A9659C946194D6CF|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

皇后區主席喬治·哈弗利預期引入地鐵到森林小丘將令皇后林蔭路化為「皇后區的[[公園大道|公園大道]]」。地鐵工程鼓勵了公寓的發展，路線完工後引誘[[曼哈頓中城|曼哈頓中城]]的居民。此站因提供可負擔的快車路線進入曼哈頓，故附近有更多的發展，令森林小丘成為更適宜居住的地方<ref name=":0" />。

1936年12月31日，IND皇后林蔭路線自前總站[[羅斯福大道／74街車站|羅斯福大道]]延長8個站至聯合公路，合共3.5英哩，而71大道車站作為此延伸線一部分啟用<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9901E2D71F3AE333A2575AC0A9619C946294D6CF|title=NEW RETAIL AREA IN QUEENS BOROUGH; Sees Roosevelt Avenue Subway Station as Great Shopping Centre. ADVANTAGES POINTED OUT Accessibility to Many Home Communities Assures Potential Market.|date=1933-07-09|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-04-26|archive-date=2016-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160512165538/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9901E2D71F3AE333A2575AC0A9619C946294D6CF|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.flickr.com/photos/127872292@N06/21882894551/|title=Reproduction Poster of Extension to Union Turnpike – Kew Gardens|website=Flickr – Photo Sharing!|access-date=2016-04-26|archive-date=2016-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160505083133/https://www.flickr.com/photos/127872292@N06/21882894551|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="WheelsDroveNY-2012">{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=qfZ0VxuLoc0C&pg=PA416|title=The Wheels That Drove New York: A History of the New York City Transit System|date=2012-08-23|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|isbn=978-3-642-30484-2|pages=416–417|author1=Roger P. Roess|author2=Gene Sansone|access-date=2017-10-03|archive-date=2016-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160516161255/https://books.google.com/books?id=qfZ0VxuLoc0C&pg=PA416|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NYTimes-RoosevelttoUTpkeOpen-10362">{{cite web|url=https://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive/pdf?res=9E06E1D91F39EE3BBC4850DFB467838D629EDE|title=PWA Party Views New Subway Link: Queens Section to Be Opened Tomorrow Is Inspected by Tuttle and Others|date=1936-12-30|website=[[紐約時報|nytimes.com]]|publisher=[[紐約時土尸十中水|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2015-06-27}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=950CE3DE143EE53ABC4950DFB467838D629EDE|title=CITY SUBWAY OPENS QUEENS LINK TODAY; Extension Brings Kew Gardens Within 36 Minutes of 42d St. on Frequent Trains.|date=1936-12-31|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-04-26|archive-date=2016-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160512162510/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=950CE3DE143EE53ABC4950DFB467838D629EDE|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9E04E1DA1F39EE3BBC4E51DFB467838D629EDE|title=OPENING MOVED UP FOR NEW SUBWAY; Traffic to Be Started on the Extension of City's Line to Kew Gardens on Thursday. EIGHT STATIONS ARE ADDED La Guardia and Official Party Will Inspect New Queens Branch on Wednesday.|date=1936-12-26|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-04-26|archive-date=2016-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160512170943/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9E04E1DA1F39EE3BBC4E51DFB467838D629EDE|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

此站在1968年{{link-en|行動計劃|Program for Action}}內一度計劃成為與從未興建的{{link-en|皇后區超級特快繞道|Queens Super-Express Bypass}}的轉乘站，並將在5個區內顯著地擴展鐵路和地鐵服務<ref name=QueensSubwayEIS-1984>{{cite book|title=Queens Subway Options Study, New York: Environmental Impact Statement|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=NaI4AQAAMAAJ&pg=PA83|accessdate=2016-07-10|date=May 1984|publisher=[[美國運輸部|United States Department of Transportation]], [[大都會運輸署|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]], {{link-en|都市大眾交通行政局|Urban Mass Transit Administration|Urban Mass Transit Administration}}|pages=83–|archive-date=2017-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170618184152/https://books.google.com/books?id=NaI4AQAAMAAJ&pg=PA83|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在1984年計劃下，新的快車站將成為[[63街線|63街線]]自[[21街-皇后橋車站_(IND_63街線)|21街-皇后橋]]東延的三個站之一，其餘兩個分別位於{{link-en|北方林蔭路|Northern Boulevard}}以及{{link-en|伍德賽德車站 (長島鐵路)|Woodside (LIRR station)|伍德賽德}}<ref name=QueensSubwayEIS-1984/>。繞道車站將設有夾層，兩個月台層（上層作為往牙買加及皇后區東南部的列車，下層作為往曼哈頓的列車使用）、新升降機入口、擴建的夾層，另有扶手電梯和樓梯連接新月台層至現有月台層<ref name=QueensSubwayEIS-1984/><ref name="ERA-TechTalk-NYCS-Feb2005"/>。新車站將建於皇后林蔭路、現時車站的南面<ref name=QueensSubwayEIS-1984/><ref name="ERA-TechTalk-NYCS-Feb2005">{{cite journal|last1=Erlitz|first1=Jeffrey|title=Tech Talk|journal=New York Division Bulletin|date=February 2005|volume=48|issue=2|pages=9–11|url=https://issuu.com/erausa/docs/2005-02-bulletin/11|accessdate=2016-07-10|publisher=Electric Railroaders Association|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816150449/https://issuu.com/erausa/docs/2005-02-bulletin/11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年，[[大都會運輸署|大都會運輸署]]為曼哈頓方向月台興建了新的信號塔。該署亦升級了此站以符合1990年[[美國殘疾人法案|美國殘疾人法案]]要求，升級包括安裝乘客升降機服務街道層、夾層和月台。該工程在延誤了三個月後<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dnainfo.com/new-york/20131231/forest-hills/forest-hills-subway-station-project-delayed-by-three-months|title=Forest Hills Subway Station Project Delayed by Three Months|work=DNAinfo New York|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209040131/http://www.dnainfo.com/new-york/20131231/forest-hills/forest-hills-subway-station-project-delayed-by-three-months|archivedate=2014-02-09}}</ref>於2014年3月完工<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dnainfo.com/new-york/20140325/forest-hills/forest-hills-subway-station-renovation-be-completed-march-mta-says|title=Forest Hills Subway Station Renovation to End in March, MTA Says|work=DNAinfo New York|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140327022909/http://www.dnainfo.com/new-york/20140325/forest-hills/forest-hills-subway-station-renovation-be-completed-march-mta-says|archivedate=2014-03-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://queens.brownstoner.com/2014/03/71st-avenue-station-renovation-in-forest-hills-will-wrap-this-month/|title=71st Avenue Station Renovation in Forest Hills will Wrap This Month|work=brownstoner.com|accessdate=2017-10-03|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040834/http://queens.brownstoner.com/2014/03/71st-avenue-station-renovation-in-forest-hills-will-wrap-this-month/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。新升降機的剪綵儀式卻拖延至2014年5月才舉行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.flickr.com/photos/mtaphotos/sets/72157644182740468/|title=Forest Hills-71st Av. ADA Elevators|work=Flickr|accessdate=2017-10-03|archive-date=2017-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170207043527/https://www.flickr.com/photos/mtaphotos/sets/72157644182740468/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

